                                      "description": "(Required) taskId returned by put or delete requests to /wiki/rest/api/content-states"
                                    }
                                  ]
                                },
                                "description": "Get Status of long running task that was previously created to set or remove content states from content.<br>User must first create a task by passing in details to /wiki/rest/api/content-states PUT or DELETE endpoints.<br><br>**[Permissions](https://confluence.atlassian.com/x/_AozKw) required**<br>Must have created long running task"
